title: EP 25 | BACHELOR & BACHELORETTE PARTIES: Best Ideas / what are the boundaries??
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description: Today we're trying to come up with some ideas for a bachelorette party for Kristen! We're also discussing bachelor and bachelorette parties as a whole. What's best? Co-ed? Are strip clubs OK? Are they not? What are the boundaries??
